title: Making Sense of Muddled QB Situations | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 352)
description:
Nyheim Hines and Cameron Brate lead this week's Initial Advice segment (0:30), and Chris Thompson and Gerald Everett are among the top players to add off waivers this week (12:00). Plus, what does the recent surge of QB benchings and injuries mean for your fantasy team? (24:30)
Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
